(jyhVw mnu`K jgq dy mUl-pRBU-ru`K nUM C`f ky aus dI rcI mwieAw-rUp) thxI nUM cMbiVAw rihMdw hY auh A`Pl hI jWdw hY (jIvn-Pl pRwpq nhIN kr skdw[)
by-smJI dy kMmW ivc pY ky-
