Awpxy mn dy ip`Cy qurn vwly mnu`K (Awqmk mOqy) mrdy hn (ies qrHW) mr ky auh AwpxI mOq ^rwb krdy hn,
ikauNik mwieAw dy moh ivc pY ky auh Awpxw Awqmk jIvn qbwh kr lYNdy hn[
Awpxy mn dy ip`Cy qurn vwlw mnu`K (ieh Dn) myrw hY (ieh prvwrw) myrw hY-in`q iehI AwK AwK ky ^uAwr huMdw rihMdw hY,
kdy Awpxy Awqmk jIvn nUM nhIN pVqwldw, mwieAw dI Btkxw ivc pY ky (Awqmk jIvn) vloN Zw&il hoieAw rihMdw hY ]1]
