pr ieh smJ pUry gurU ny (iksy ivrly nUM) b^SI hY ]2]
ijs mnu`K dw mn hr vyly mwieAw dy moh ivc Btkdw hY auh moh dIAW s`tW KWdw rihMdw hY[
